title: Dale Watson & The Lone Stars - El Rancho Azul (2013)
description: If you refuse to acknowledge hot country, bro country or whatever sh1t Nash Vegas is slinging these days then this is for you. Turn it up, grab yer pardner, close your eyes and pretend you're at the Broken Spoke for some two-stepping. My favorite tune here is 'Where Do You Want It?" written by Dale to commemorate Billy Joe Shaver taking out the trash in the parking lot of Papa Joe's several years ago
